{"tid":2426500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安徽女蘋果官網花逾萬購iPhone 12　到手竟變蒙牛蘋果味酸酸乳","createTime":"2021-02-28T06:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T10:55:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25888a2e8f121c524997e104822a55daf5090db5","tid":2426500,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"安徽合肥一名女子近日花上10099元（人民幣，下同）在蘋果官網上買了一台iPhone 12 pro max手機，但當她收到速遞後拆開一看，裡面竟然只有一瓶過期的蒙牛蘋果味酸酸乳。<br />\n<br />\n據內媒報道，劉女士16日在蘋果官方網站上買了一部iPhone 12 pro max手機，她在收貨地址上寫的是她居住的小區。劉女18日接到速遞員的電話，稱手機包裹已經抵達該小區。因劉女當時不在家，劉女提出要當面簽收，但速遞員表示可以存放在小區的速遞櫃中，劉女便沒有堅持要當面簽收。<br />\n<br />\n當天晚上，劉女從速遞櫃取出包裹。劉女發現，包裹裡面沒有手機的蹤影，卻有一盒外表非常骯髒、並已過期的250ml蒙牛蘋果味酸酸乳。劉女指，她是從速遞盒的封條處打開的，當時那盒蒙牛酸酸乳是固定在膠條裡面的。<br />\n<br />\n劉女對速遞盒仔細檢查後，發現速遞盒的外觀上沒有什麼被破壞的地方，但是拆開盒子後在包裹側面，有幾處疑似破壞的痕跡。同時，速遞盒內的透明固定條有明顯的被拉扯的痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n劉女隨後報警，並向速遞公司和蘋果方面反映。在27日下午，一名自稱是郵政的工作人員告知劉女，「本應發給她的手機已被激活」，但對於劉女所遇問題的處理，依然未明確回應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210228/442697933943476224293106.jpeg/zovLIQAUgpWd5r6dSXUtyUAEU4vXcq0h0bKVJ9GylSc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210228%2F442697933943476224293106.jpeg%2FzovLIQAUgpWd5r6dSXUtyUAEU4vXcq0h0bKVJ9GylSc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=43c47c1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b75a8c512e9aa8368dcf65ac07f82baf70661a03","tid":2426500,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:42:48.000Z","msg":"畜遞<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7a99e934b62fb6c3f44f86205064bf2efe2c67","tid":2426500,"uid":142358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:42:53.000Z","msg":"IMilk<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589f1b43c3a60789a0f234d1a6da7a908addd094","tid":2426500,"uid":104962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">This</span></span>"},{"pid":"ac4d5f0ab2106f15a3ca0bef1aca5668fe0713e3","tid":2426500,"uid":301529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:46:05.000Z","msg":"未來香港"},{"pid":"f36b3955d5b99671247f7f89f5491f9c03b32c69","tid":2426500,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:49:28.000Z","msg":"又中鐵拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af4b0e15ea36394dbb404587e5aed3a699b7561","tid":2426500,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac4d5f0ab2106f15a3ca0bef1aca5668fe0713e3","tid":2426500,"uid":301529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:46:05.000Z","msg":"未來香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba846b101362312aec87ff319c6452c7e7adf224","tid":2426500,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"比支蘋果汁咪算有良心"},{"pid":"7173e2f4a9e5b7e84832702ad91887eab04a8080","tid":2426500,"uid":55924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"屌 好想去做速遞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fda4d0426874e5697b4b09e75e4f0716bf56dc","tid":2426500,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:52:08.000Z","msg":"似連登仔啲聖誕濕鳩交換禮物嘅屎橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eea81b87848ad85375b9b09d95dd1f52f28f3d1","tid":2426500,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba846b101362312aec87ff319c6452c7e7adf224","tid":2426500,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"比支蘋果汁咪算有良心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:54:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">已過期</span></span>"},{"pid"